CVE-2024-46669 has been assigned to this vulnerability. A CVSS v3 base score of 3.5 has been calculated; the CVSS vector string is (CVSS:3.1/AV:A/AC:L/PR:L/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:L).
3.2.6 OUT-OF-BOUNDS READ CWE-125
